{"tid":809082,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 換咗mon唔正常","createTime":"2018-09-07T01:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T04:51:08.000Z","uid":73399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b6e984dbd8f3c0c3acfaa3959978ae2eb49d7b3","tid":809082,"uid":73399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T01:02:16.000Z","msg":"呢排電腦換咗個 Philips 227E4LH mon<br />\n由VGA頭換咗做兩邊HDMI線<br />\n機同mon都冇壞<br />\n但係就有以下問題<br />\n<br />\n1. Boot 機過完windows畫面後會黑mon，出咗個&rdquo;Check cable connection&ldquo;既message，但係熄mon再著又正常顯示入咗windows既畫面。初步諗係入 windows 前後 resolution 唔同既問題 (入windows後係1920*1080)，但係試過入安全模式較返1920*1080都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 開facebook如果load到有片既位，會黑一黑mon，大概一秒左右會自動著返。諗緊係咪個mon既refresh rate問題，但係較到50Hertz 都係會間唔中出現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實會唔會係條 HDMI 線有問題？<br />\nJJ插冰求救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba680157d7fb29b570839f4d06487ef68f8f91f","tid":809082,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"1 我遇過,最後搵新機試...係DISPLAY卡插頭問題<br />\n<br />\n2 唔知,如果係用返HDMI頭發生,咁應該係同上問題,除左轉插口或者UPDATE DRIVER就係睇下張卡有無過保"},{"pid":"cfae99b392749261d1bf4a651337c959d76e6c56","tid":809082,"uid":73399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba680157d7fb29b570839f4d06487ef68f8f91f","tid":809082,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"1 我遇過,最後搵新機試...係DISPLAY卡插頭問題<br />\n<br />\n2 唔知,如果係用返HDMI頭發生,咁應該係同上問題,除左轉插口或者UPDATE DRIVER就係睇下張卡有無過保"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"我試下買過條VGA線試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}